Spot Instances should be avoided if a workload cannot accept interruption if capacity becomes temporarily unavailable.

Snowball Edge devices have endpoints compatible with Amazon S3, Amazon EC2 and Amazon Machine Images AMI. This allows for programmatic use cases. 
